  "text": "Maternal smoking is an important risk factor for low birth weight and preterm birth [CITATION_1] and also constitutes a potential risk factor for thyroid dysfunction [CITATION_2] . Our results, however, did not show signs of confounding by smoking. , 1980 -1982, 1983 -1985, 1986 -1988, 1989 -1991, 1992 -1994, 1995 -1997, 1998 -2000, 2001 -2003, 2004 -2006 ",
